{"tid":1352153,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣返工阿？老闆？","createTime":"2019-07-22T17:41:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T00:18:54.000Z","uid":38177,"like":89,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"9c02d7efafb9f34317df26d6970d2f913432ef71","tid":1352153,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:41:14.000Z","msg":"721元朗恐襲喎，警察又無人到，落哂閘，你無睇新聞？<br />\n<br />\n如果係個別事件，啲鋪頭又點會落哂閘？<br />\n<br />\n返工ja，搵條命同你博？人工又無得加，又無OT錢<br />\n之前就話拍硬檔同你OT搞埋啲手尾先走，宜家你攞埋我條命？<br />\n<br />\n我好撚驚阿，點知會唔會搭搭下港鐵又比人打？又點知啲黑社會會唔會顛到攔巴士攔小巴再打人？<br />\n唔洗驚？你又點知會無事？<br />\n我比人打你賠償我損失？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">人命值幾錢？你點賠阿？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你當我AL好，曠工又好，總之香港未安全，我邊度都唔去</span>"},{"pid":"371c30696d3f203369a30da7f542c7515a1f815c","tid":1352153,"uid":104767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:42:39.000Z","msg":"我想返工但唔敢出門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f489df49921ae5ac1a595d9ee9c3724f6a5d1847","tid":1352153,"uid":199727,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:42:55.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"ab4b27cbe53f634d29039b63100786715d880432","tid":1352153,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:43:06.000Z","msg":"咁我叫我返工？我打工炸，你估我賣命？"},{"pid":"989595086ae51a75c1c15f4e967507957b443e32","tid":1352153,"uid":285330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:43:41.000Z","msg":"地鐵不合作運動係唯一贏既方法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1343910\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1343910</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"47fd6ac7ee6f27f16bb5c1fedbd1b05bf7af0e67","tid":1352153,"uid":38177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ab4b27cbe53f634d29039b63100786715d880432","tid":1352153,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:43:06.000Z","msg":"咁我叫我返工？我打工炸，你估我賣命？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:43:4